longBusinessSummary: Hiru Corporation, through its subsidiary, produces Chinese herbs for the naturopathic industry in China. It manufactures herbal supplements containing ginseng. The company sells and distributes pharmaceuticals, health and beauty products, dietary and herbal supplements, and other healthcare products. It manufactures approximately 120 extracts used in traditional Chinese medicine. Hiru Corporation sells its products through regional distributors, as well as directly to the hospitals, clinics, and pharmacies in China. Hiru Corporation was formerly known as Phoenix Restaurant Group, Inc. and changed its name to Hiru Corporation in November 2008. The company is based in Henderson, Nevada.
